        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-09-20 10:04:40.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nfrom the moment you certify a resource the vf name can't be updated.",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "39f3a0397ee49d39d7b266e7f86ca80ae9261728",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 2125,
          "name": "Priyanshu Agarwal",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "pagarwal@amdocs.com",
          "username": "priyanshua"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-09-20 10:16:28.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nHi Michael,\n\nThe issue here arrives even before certifying the VF. If we try to change the name of VF before certifying than it doesn't work if there are any operations created in side it. There is a bug in VF operation handling which causes this.\n\nThanks\nPriyanshu",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "46d83430c8f9e03ec0257e84960e4b4c8638a14a",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 69,
          "name": "Michael Lando",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "michael.lando@intl.att.com",
          "username": "ml636r"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-09-24 13:23:10.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nthank you for the clarification so the issue is connected only to operate in case the vf name was changed right?",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "029e1a4f41b937236406a26afc9faf3dc568acde",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 2125,
          "name": "Priyanshu Agarwal",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "pagarwal@amdocs.com",
          "username": "priyanshua"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-09-24 15:26:17.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nHi Michael, In our analysis we found that the PUT call on any modification on VF (created from VSP) fails if the VF contains atleast 1 workflow operation.",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "e0c96ebc5de1a16ce2e28e0d0dcb807f65a9a161",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 2125,
          "name": "Priyanshu Agarwal",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "pagarwal@amdocs.com",
          "username": "priyanshua"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-09-25 05:58:48.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nHi Michael,\nPlease ignore my previous comment. You are right, the issue only happens if the VF name is changed.\nThanks\nPriyanshu",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
